message.body: I skipped Morgan today. I needed the sleep! Want to go to Angie's class with me? How was limbs??

I've got a reading group at seven :-( -I'm going to try my first spinning class at the penn gym this afternoon. Wish me luck! Limbs was less grim than last week, which is good I guess. I bet it was your good vibes!xxx

Aw. Well I might be pirating (I tried to type pilating but the iPhone made me a sailor) more often so we can have our five minutes of glory before limbs. :) spin spin--that's awesome! Have fun! Watch your knees. Don't let them flare! xxxxxxxxxxxxx
PS: the men's soccer coach is super hot but just made a joke about our little British intern who is British out of a movie. It's ridiculous!!!
